      <scopecontent id="aspace_ccd12239e99d83fdab6834f611f61a7c">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection consists of stage lighting company catalogs that document developments in stage lighting equipment from the early 1920s through 1970. Represented in the collection are manufacturers from the United States and Great Britain, including Century Lighting, Kliegl Brothers, Strand Electric &amp; Engineering Co. Ltd., and Ward Leonard Electric Co. The collection also includes a selected lighting bibliography from circa 1880-1940.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_13e5ab111aa90dd2b90ab885b65a4fe4">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Organized into two series: Series I. Stage Lighting Catalogs. Series II. Selected Lighting Bibliography.</p>  
      </arrangement>
